headline: Down 30% in 2025, Is This Dividend King a No-Brainer Stock to Buy Now?
summary: Target is on track for another year of lower earnings.  Inventory levels are inflated because Target overestimated consumer demand.  Target has to deliver better results or the stock could keep falling as investors lose patience.
